    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the high-strung S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This example delivers a visceral 8,000 RPM redline through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.62-ratio limited-slip differential. To ensure chassis longevity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced\u2014critical preventative measures for this platform. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the aesthetics reflect a vehicle enjoyed on the open road, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, offering a pure analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
